In order to do so the entries should be changed from

--snip--
&quot;key_short_Meta&quot;:[{&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;key_short_Meta&quot;:&quot;Meta&quot;},&quot;target&quot;:&quot;i18n&quot;}]
--snip--

to (for e.g. german version)

--snip--
&quot;key_short_Meta&quot;:[{&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;key_short_Meta&quot;:&quot;Meta&quot;},&quot;target&quot;:&quot;i18n-de&quot;}]
--snip--</thetext>
